text: In the promotion for this week's episode of "The Late Late Show with James Corden," Corden and his guest, Maroon 5 singer Adam Levine, get pulled over by a Los Angeles County Sheriff's deputy for causing a traffic hazard. Screenshot from Youtube
title: James Corden, Adam Levine stopped for causing traffic hazard

twitter.title: James Corden, Adam Levine stopped during Carpool Karaoke for ‘causing a traffic hazard’
twitter.description: James Corden and Adam Levine were filming an episode of Carpool Karaoke when they were pulled over by a Los Angeles County Sheriff’s deputy for “causing a traffic hazard.” Footage of the stop will air on Corden’s show on Friday, May 25, 2018.
